Financial Services Cloud
Manage Standing Instructions Service Process (Unmanaged Package)
The Manage Standing Instructions service process allows your customers to add or modify instructions for setting up recurring and timely payments.

Available in: Lightning Experience, Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled

Setup and Configuration of the Manage Standing Instructions Service Process
Add a Standing Instruction to an Account
Use the Service Process Studio to enable the Manage Standing Instructions service process.
Capture and submit a request for adding a standing instruction through the Manage Standing Instructions OmniScript. A case is then created in Salesforce.
title: Managing Standing Instructions in Financial Services Cloud
